dct_title_s: Automobile road from Bakersfield and vicinity to San Luis Obispo
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; WLM.
Relief shown by hachures and text (grade %).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, gates.
Indicates distances from Bakersfield and San Luis Obispo.
Numbered 102 at bottom of map andn 6 in right margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
